regarded symposium for professors of rhetoric and composition  and several presentations on Post each year featuring writers in all genres  For more information  see the Institute Director of Writing  232 Scott Shipp Hall    Back to Top   Print Degree Planner   Print Friendly Page   All catalogues   2016 Virginia Military Institute  Powered by the Acalog  Academic Catalog Management System   ACMS  Mobile Site 